      "body_lines": [
        "A special discussion between the Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa and former President Maithripala Sirisena was held today at the office of the Leader of the Opposition.",
        "The Office of the Leader of the Opposition said that the meeting was held as part of the National Reform and Future Plan."
